@startuml
title Import Pipeline - API und Application
actor User
participant ImportsController
participant ExcelImportAnalysisService
participant ImportCoordinator
participant IImportReader
participant IImportMapper
participant IImportValidator
participant DuplicationCheckService
participant ApplyResolutionService
participant ImportCommitService
participant ImportWriteGate
participant IImportWriter
participant IRawZoneWriter
participant IImportReportRepository
User -> ImportsController : analyze workbook
ImportsController -> ExcelImportAnalysisService
ExcelImportAnalysisService -> IImportReader
ExcelImportAnalysisService -> IImportMapper
ExcelImportAnalysisService -> IImportValidator
ExcelImportAnalysisService -> DuplicationCheckService
ExcelImportAnalysisService -> IImportReportRepository : persist report/issues/audit
User -> ImportsController : resolutions
ImportsController -> ApplyResolutionService
User -> ImportsController : commit
ImportsController -> ImportCommitService
ImportCommitService -> ImportWriteGate
ImportCommitService -> IImportWriter : Database or Excel adapter
ImportCommitService -> IRawZoneWriter : optional original file
note right : Silver/Gold-Zonen sind konzeptionell,\nnicht als eigene technische Speicheradapter implementiert.
@enduml
